THIS COPY OF NEVADA COBOL IS CONFIGURED TO RUN ON CPM SYSTEMS.

Nevada COBOL will work on both AMSTRAD CPM2.2 and CPM3.1 systems, but
will require terminal installation according to the instructions set
out in the manual.

A text editor will be required: ED will be OK - but we strongly recommend 
that you use NewWord (a wordstar compatible with many additional features)
for all program editing and ASCII Wordprocessing.

